title: For Sale/Trade:  ***ATTN ALL SELLERS & BUYERS*** LEGAL UPDATE!!!
location: THE CAPITOL CITY, North Carolina, United States
postcontent:
For all individuals selling long guns in NC. Contrary to popular belief, you do not need a concealed carry permit, hundgun purchase permit, or even a North Carolina state ID to buy or sell rifles & shotguns face to face in a private sale. Those laws apply to HANDGUNS ONLY!

If you are a state resident or from out of state and dont have a NC ID but want to buy a rifle/shotgun: as long as you are 18+ and not a convicted felon or have been dishonorably discharged or have denounced your US citizenship, ANY OF THE 50 STATES' ID is all you need regardless of what the seller says. The reason Dick's, Walmart, and many FFL's want that documentation is for corporate liability mitigation only. Ask them and they will tell you it is company policy. There is no law existing requiring any special paperwork for long guns.

title: For Sale:  CMMG -- AR-15 300 Blackout WASP .300 5-Mags Layaway
postcontent: sporting, combat, and law enforcement. The CMMG AR rifle offered in this auction features a WASP (Weapon Armament Surface Protection) treated barrel - a salt bath ferritic nitrocarburizing surface conversion process or more commonly referred to as nitriding. The nitriding conversion is applied to the barrel inside and out, along with the front sight base on our LE rifles and uppers. Nitriding offers improved wear, abrasion, and corrosion resistance when compared to hard chrome lining or phosphating. Unlike chrome lining, where the chrome is built up on the surface, nitriding converts the surface without the risk of dimensional build up. CMMG Pioneered the use of this nitriding process on AR barrels – it is the State of the Art. The rifle also features a forged upper receiver, RDIAS/RLL compatible forged lower, Mil-Spec lower parts kit (.250 takedown and .154 FCG pins), mid-length gas system, 30-round Magpul PMAG, and it will accept standard AR15 mags with either 300AAC Blackout or 300 Whisper ammo.  You won’t find a better made AR rifle in the smokin’ hot 300 Blackout caliber anywhere!
